                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-mms                 .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Start errata : ad uscita                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to stp-srt-inp-ubi-900.
