           move      "SE"                 to   f-ope                  .
           perform   det-zos-dcp-cll-000  thru det-zos-dcp-cll-999    .
           if        f-sts                =    e-not-err
                     go to stp-srt-inp-ubi-600
           else      go to stp-srt-inp-ubi-200.
       stp-srt-inp-ubi-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Preparazione record di Sort                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione iniziale                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   srt-rec                .
