      *                  * Chiave di sort                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Numero d'ordine progressivo di rilascio *
      *                      * al sort                                 *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-srt-num-dop          .
           move      w-srt-num-dop        to   srt-num-dop            .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Dati di sort                                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Record [dcp]                            *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      rf-dcp               to   srt-rec-dcp            .
       stp-srt-inp-ubi-700.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Rilascio del record al Sort                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           release   srt-rec                                          .
       stp-srt-inp-ubi-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Riciclo                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     stp-srt-inp-ubi-200.




       stp-srt-inp-ubi-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     stp-srt-inp-ubi-999.
       stp-srt-inp-ubi-999.
           exit.

